## .env Setup — Both Key Systems

```bash
# ── NEW PROJECTS (post-November 2025) ──────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://[ref].supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=sb_publishable_...  # safe to expose
SUPABASE_SECRET_KEY=sb_secret_...                         # NEVER expose, NEVER commit

# ── LEGACY PROJECTS (pre-November 2025) ────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://[ref].supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJ...                      # JWT, safe to expose
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJ...                           # NEVER expose, NEVER commit

# Both systems: add to .gitignore if not already there
# .env.local is git-ignored by default in Next.js
```

