## Edge Functions — New Pre-populated Secret Names

```typescript
// Edge Functions — new projects use different pre-populated secret names
// OLD (legacy projects):
Deno.env.get('SUPABASE_ANON_KEY')           // → anon JWT
Deno.env.get('SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY')   // → service_role JWT

// NEW (post-Nov 2025 projects):
Deno.env.get('SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY')    // → sb_publishable_...
Deno.env.get('SUPABASE_SECRET_KEY')         // → sb_secret_...

// Safe pattern — works with BOTH systems:
const anonKey = Deno.env.get('SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY')
             ?? Deno.env.get('SUPABASE_ANON_KEY')
             ?? ''

const serviceKey = Deno.env.get('SUPABASE_SECRET_KEY')
                ?? Deno.env.get('SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY')
                ?? ''
```

