## Migrating a Legacy Project to New Keys (Optional — Non-Breaking)

```
1. Dashboard → Settings → API → API Keys → "Add new publishable key"
   Supabase generates the new sb_publishable_... and sb_secret_... keys
   Both old AND new keys work simultaneously during migration

2. Update .env.local:
   NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=sb_publishable_...
   SUPABASE_SECRET_KEY=sb_secret_...
   (keep old keys as fallback during transition)

3. Update Netlify environment variables with new key names

4. Deploy and verify — old keys still work until you remove them

5. Remove old keys from Dashboard when confident
```

